  <content>
    <description>
      <levelledPara>
        <title>Scheduled Maintenance Intervals</title>
        <para>This Data Module defines the scheduled maintenance intervals for time-limited tasks and periodic maintenance checks under ATA Chapter 05.</para>
      </levelledPara>
      
      <levelledPara>
        <title>Interval Types</title>
        <para>Maintenance intervals are categorized by:</para>
        <para>
          <randomList>
            <listItem>
              <para><emphasis>Calendar-based intervals</emphasis>: Tasks scheduled by calendar time (days, months, years)</para>
            </listItem>
            <listItem>
              <para><emphasis>Flight-hour-based intervals</emphasis>: Tasks scheduled by cumulative flight hours</para>
            </listItem>
            <listItem>
              <para><emphasis>Cycle-based intervals</emphasis>: Tasks scheduled by flight cycles (takeoff/landing)</para>
            </listItem>
            <listItem>
              <para><emphasis>Condition-based intervals</emphasis>: Tasks triggered by system condition monitoring</para>
            </listItem>
          </randomList>
        </para>
      </levelledPara>
      
      <levelledPara>
        <title>Standard Intervals</title>
        <table>
          <tgroup cols="4">
            <colspec colname="c1"/>
            <colspec colname="c2"/>
            <colspec colname="c3"/>
            <colspec colname="c4"/>
            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry>Task Code</entry>
                <entry>Description</entry>
                <entry>Interval Type</entry>
                <entry>Interval Value</entry>
              </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry>ATA-05-001</entry>
                <entry>Daily inspection</entry>
                <entry>Calendar</entry>
                <entry>24 hours</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>ATA-05-002</entry>
                <entry>Weekly inspection</entry>
                <entry>Calendar</entry>
                <entry>7 days</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>ATA-05-003</entry>
                <entry>Monthly inspection</entry>
                <entry>Calendar</entry>
                <entry>30 days</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>ATA-05-004</entry>
                <entry>100-hour inspection</entry>
                <entry>Flight hours</entry>
                <entry>100 FH</entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
      </levelledPara>
      
      <levelledPara>
        <title>ESG Integration</title>
        <para>All scheduled maintenance activities include ESG impact tracking:</para>
        <para>
          <randomList>
            <listItem>
              <para>Material consumption and waste generation metrics</para>
            </listItem>
            <listItem>
              <para>Energy usage during maintenance operations</para>
            </listItem>
            <listItem>
              <para>Environmental impact of consumables and fluids</para>
            </listItem>
            <listItem>
              <para>Worker safety and ergonomics considerations</para>
            </listItem>
          </randomList>
        </para>
      </levelledPara>
      
      <levelledPara>
        <title>References</title>
